	You get a +2 bonus on all <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/jum=
p.htm">Jump</a> checks and <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/tum=
ble.htm">Tumble</a> checks.
</p>

