	You get a +2 bonus on all <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/bal=
ance.htm">Balance</a> checks and <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skil=
ls/escapeArtist.htm">Escape Artist</a> checks.
</p>

<h3 id=3D"alertness">Alertness [General]</h3>

<h5>Benefit</h5>
<p>
	You get a +2 bonus on all <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/lis=
ten.htm">Listen</a> checks and <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills=
/spot.htm">Spot</a> checks.
