	You can get one extra attack per round with a ranged weapon. The attack is=
 at your highest base attack bonus, but each attack you make in that round =
(the extra one and the normal ones) takes a -2 penalty. You must use the <a=
 href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/combat/actionsInCombat.htm#fullAttack">=
full attack</a> action to use this feat.
