	<a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/barbarian.htm">Barbarians</a=
>, <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/bard.htm">bards</a>, <a hr=
ef=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/cleric.htm">clerics</a>, <a href=
=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/druid.htm">druids</a>, <a href=3D"ht=
tps://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/fighter.htm">fighters</a>, <a href=3D"http=
s://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/paladin.htm">paladins</a>, and <a href=3D"ht=
tps://www.d20srd.org/srd/classes/ranger.htm">rangers</a> automatically have=
 Shield Proficiency as a bonus feat. They need not select it.
