ect Stunning Fist as a bonus feat at 1st level, even if she does not meet t=
he prerequisites. A monk who selects this feat may attempt a stunning attac=
k a number of times per day equal to her monk level, plus one more time per=
 day for every four levels she has in classes other than monk.
